<subSubSection id="C3136559FFC1FFC0F82EFAABEF2AFA07" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB636D2FFC1FFC0F82EFAABEF2AFA07" blockId="4.[2020,2610,1225,1651]" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">
The systematic status of this speciesis still very doubtful, as it is known only from the type specimen. It belongs to the 
<taxonomicName id="4C094D51FFC1FFC0F606FAD1EE0FFA56" authorityName="Osgood" authorityYear="1932" class="Mammalia" family="Cervidae" genus="Muntiacus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="rooseveltorum">rooseveltorum</taxonomicName>
species complex;it could be simply a synonym of M. 
<taxonomicName id="4C094D51FFC1FFC0F72FFA0EEFA3FA2F" baseAuthorityName="Giao, Tuoc, Eric [Wikramanayake], Dung et al. in Ha" baseAuthorityYear="1997" box="[2276,2462,1465,1494]" class="Mammalia" family="Cervidae" genus="Muntiacus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="truongsonensis">truongsonensis</taxonomicName>
or 
<taxonomicName id="4C094D51FFC1FFC0F618FA0EEE51FA07" authorityName="Osgood" authorityYear="1932" class="Mammalia" family="Cervidae" genus="Muntiacus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="rooseveltorum">M. rooseveltorum</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3136559FFC1FFC0F82EF9BFEEAEF9B4" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" type="distribution">
<caption id="DF76665AFFC1FFC0F82EF9BFEEAEF9B4" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6514413" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6514413" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6514413/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" targetBox="[1404,1997,1235,1650]" targetPageId="4">
<paragraph id="8BB636D2FFC1FFC0F82EF9BFEEAEF9B4" blockId="4.[2020,2610,1225,1651]" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="B97DEAC0FFC1FFC0F82EF9BFEEA8F9DC" bold="true" box="[2021,2197,1544,1573]" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">Distribution.</emphasis>
NW 
<collectingCountry id="F31E7642FFC1FFC0F710F9BFEF68F9DC" box="[2267,2389,1544,1573]" name="Vietnam" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
; possibly neighboring 
<collectingCountry id="F31E7642FFC1FFC0F786F987EEB2F9B4" box="[2125,2191,1584,1613]" name="Laos" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">Laos</collectingCountry>
