</paragraph>
</caption>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3136559FFC1FFC0F82EF9E5E0ADF93D" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BB636D2FFC1FFC0F82EF9E5E0ADF93D" blockId="4.[2020,2610,1225,1651]" lastBlockId="4.[1405,2608,1659,2086]" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="B97DEAC0FFC1FFC0F82EF9E5EEE2F98A" bold="true" box="[2021,2271,1618,1651]" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">Descriptive notes.</emphasis>
No specific body measurements available. Small-sized, morphologically similar to the Annamite Muntjac. The coat is reddish.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3136559FFC1FFC0FAB4F97EEFCAF913" box="[1407,2551,1737,1770]" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" type="biology_ecology">
