<emphasis id="B97DEAC0FFC1FFC0FAB4F97EE3D3F913" bold="true" box="[1407,1518,1737,1770]" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">Habitat.</emphasis>
Recorded in closed canopy evergreen forest above 
<quantity id="4CF19B37FFC1FFC0F70FF97EEF24F913" box="[2244,2329,1737,1770]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" unit="m" value="900.0">900 m</quantity>
above sea level.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3136559FFC1FFC0FAB4F947E173F8C0" pageId="4" pageNumber="411" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph id="8BB636D2FFC1FFC0FAB4F947E173F8C0" blockId="4.[1405,2608,1659,2086]" pageId="4" pageNumber="411">
